  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 ; 5 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Bus collides with people waiting for fuel in Batticaloa; 5 people were injured",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Five persons were seriously injured when a bus collided with a group of people waiting for fuel at the Batticaloa Urani petrol station this morning (7).",
        "People have been queuing with motorcycles at the petrol station on the Colombo-Batticaloa main road since last evening for fuel.",
        "At around 5.00 am on Monday, a private bus carrying workers from a garment factory in the Chengaladi area to Arayambathi collided head-on with a truck waiting for fuel.",
        "Five people were injured in the accident and were admitted to the Modhu Teaching Hospital. The bus driver left the bus and fled.",
        "Five motorcycles were damaged in the incident and the bus was taken to the police station and steps have been taken to arrest the driver, police said."
      ],
